SelfSurveys,enables,businesses,to,implement,reliable,automated,information,gathering,surveys,which,can,easily,collect,analyze,and,compare,vital,business,data,from,any,desktop,computer,laptop,PDA,or,PC,Companion,mobile,device,SelfSurveys,provides,a,full,arsenal,of,intelligence,gathering,support,services,that,allow,teams,to,make,better,business,decisions,faster,than,permitted,using,traditional,research,techniques,All,of,SelfSurveys,functions,can,be,accessed,programmatically,for,integration,with,other,applications,using,a,SOAP,based,API